title: Jaguars topple Titans as Minshew Mania rolls on (Football 9/20)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap Thursday Night Football and the Jags winning effort over the Titans. The guys discuss Gardner Minshew's performance (2:00), Marcus Mariota's struggles (4:00), Jacksonville's chances in the AFC South (15:00), Jalen Ramsey's future (19:00), the possibility of Mike Leach in the NFL (29:00), and the officiating on Thursday (33:00).
